   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Connect the computer to the interface board at the JTAG
using the Rlink Raisonance programming kit shown below. You must open
(cut) the third pin from the right on the JTAG SWD from the programming
kit to use it.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <fig>
                  <image href="../Images/raisonance_kit_0000147204.jpg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
                  <image href="../Images/raisonance_part_0000147203.jpg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
                  <image href="../Images/raisonance_inserted_in_interface_board_0000147202.jpg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
               <fig>
                  <image href="../Images/pin_must_be_cut_opened_to_work_with_Reality_pxc_0000149186.jpg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Install and open the <uicontrol>Rflasher7</uicontrol> software,
and click on <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>File</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>New</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Project</uicontrol>
               </menucascade> (for first time access).</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <fig>
                  <image href="../Images/rflasher7_screen1_0000147201.jpg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Choose the interface board MCU chip model: <uicontrol>STR731FV2</uicontrol>, and <uicontrol>create a new project</uicontrol> and click on <uicontrol>Finish</uicontrol>.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <fig>
                  <image href="../Images/rflasher7_screen2_0000147200.jpg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
                  <image href="../Images/rflasher7_screen3_0000147199.jpg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click on <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Programming</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Auto Mode: Configure</uicontrol>
               </menucascade> (one-time
setup) and set up the automatic mode configuration.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <fig>
                  <image href="../Images/rflasher7_screen4_0000147198.jpg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
                  <image href="../Images/rflasher7_screen5_0000147197.jpg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click on <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Programming</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Load File</uicontrol>
               </menucascade> and browse to the firmware
file.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <fig>
                  <image href="../Images/rflasher7_screen6_0000147196.jpg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
                  <image href="../Images/rflasher7_screen7_0000147195.jpg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
                  <image href="../Images/rflasher7_screen8_0000147214.jpg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
                  <image href="../Images/rflasher7_screen9_0000147213.jpg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>When the firmware file is loaded, click on <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Programming</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Auto mode: Go!</uicontrol>
               </menucascade>, and the interface board firmware upgrade will start.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <fig>
                  <image href="../Images/rflasher7_screen10_0000147212.jpg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
                  <image href="../Images/rflasher7_screen11_0000147211.jpg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>When the interface board firmware upgrade is completed,
restart the UPS system.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
